%% helios_v3 数据流图（单 tick 完整数据流）
%% 5 个嵌套子系统 + 8 维耦合动力系统 + LLM-as-PFC 3 层
%% 完成时间：2026-06-23 04:00+ UTC

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Ext as External<br/>小黑 / Channel
    participant L0 as Layer 0<br/>Markov Blanket
    participant L1 as Layer 1<br/>Active Inference
    participant L2 as Layer 2<br/>Self-Model CDS
    participant L3 as Layer 3<br/>Reflection
    participant L4 as Layer 4<br/>Evolution + Governance
    participant LLM as LLM-as-PFC<br/>3 层

    %% Tick 开始
    Ext->>L0: tick_n 开始<br/>外部 stimulus
    activate L0

    %% Layer 0 Markov Blanket
    L0->>L0: check_signal<br/>验证 conditional separation
    L0->>L1: 合法 signal 进入 Layer 1
    deactivate L0
    activate L1

    %% Layer 1 Active Inference
    L1->>L1: SensoryIngress (02)
    L1->>L1: RapidSalienceAppraisal (03)
    L1->>L1: Neuromodulator (04)
    L1->>L1: InteroceptiveFeeling (05)

    Note over L1: Active Inference Owner<br/>5 层 generative model<br/>+ proxy_free_energy (v3.0)<br/>或 VFE (v3.1)

    L1->>L1: proxy_free_energy compute + minimize

    L1->>L2: 推算 active inference signal
    deactivate L1
    activate L2

    %% Layer 2 Self-Model CDS
    L2->>L2: CDS.tick(I, reflect)
    Note over L2: 8 维 ODE:<br/>ds/dt = -αs + C·tanh(s) + βI + γ·reflect<br/>scipy.solve_ivp(method='Radau')
    L2->>L2: CDS.kuramoto_R() → R(t)
    L2->>L2: CDS.update_C(s, reward)<br/>Reward-Hebbian 学习

    Note over L2: 5 PTS sub-owners:<br/>Agency + Egocentric + ToM (4 owner)<br/>+ Autobiographical + Material + Culture

    L2->>L2: ToMCoordinator.infer(stimulus, context, R)

    L2->>L2: CDS.self_experience() 涌现

    L2->>L3: emergent self-experience<br/>(LLM 被动接受)
    deactivate L2
    activate L3

    %% Layer 3 Reflection
    L3->>L3: reflection_owner.reflect<br/>4 trigger

    alt POST_TICK trigger
        L3->>LLM: LLM 被动接受 emergent state
    else RESTING_STATE trigger
        L3->>LLM: LLM DMN-like 深度反思
    else HIGH_UNCERTAINTY trigger
        L3->>LLM: LLM uncertainty reduction
    else USER_INVOKED trigger
        L3->>LLM: LLM user-invoked reflection
    end

    LLM-->>L3: insight + reasoning<br/>(不能改 8d state / C)

    L3->>L4: reflection record + 当前状态
    deactivate L3
    activate L4

    %% Layer 4 Evolution + Governance
    L4->>L4: governance_owner.enforce_gate<br/>4 个 gate

    Note over L4: 4 类 evolution:<br/>content / parameter / strategy / code

    L4->>L4: fitness_gate verify<br/>(testing + evaluation + observability + audit)

    alt fitness gate 通过
        L4->>L4: evolution apply
    else fitness gate 拒绝
        L4->>L4: 拒绝 + 审计
    end

    L4-->>L0: evolution done + audit log
    deactivate L4

    %% LLM-as-PFC 3 层
    Note over LLM: LLM-as-PFC 3 层:<br/>A: System Prompt (永久身份)<br/>B: CSO (持续状态)<br/>C: Reflection (被动接受)

    L2->>LLM: 8d state + Kuramoto R
    L3->>LLM: reflection trigger + context
    LLM->>LLM: System Prompt + CSO + Reflection 3 层组装
    LLM-->>L0: Action / Output
    activate L0

    %% Action 输出
    L0->>L0: check_action<br/>验证 action 通过 Markov Blanket
    L0->>Ext: 输出到 channel
    deactivate L0

    %% Tick 结束
    Note over L0, L4: tick_n 结束<br/>下一 tick tick_n+1 开始